Program: Discovery
Title: 100 Years of X-Rays
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrwjn
Last Broadcast Date: 03 November 1995
Special edition commemorating 100 years of X-rays, discovered in 1895 by Wilhelm Rontgen. The footsteps of the early researchers are traced, and medical imaging's revolutionising of diagnosis and treatment is examined. Presenter unknown.